(10, 12, 'Sunday Special', 'Enjoy Sweet Sunday ', 'sunday-special', '<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:600px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="3">\r\n			<h2>[SUBJECT]</h2>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Hi [USER],<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			Sunday, being the day of the Sun, as the name of the first day of the week, is derived from Egyptian astrology, where the seven planets, known in English as Saturn, Jupiter, Mars, the Sun, Venus, Mercury and the Moon, each had an hour of the day assigned to them, and the planet which was regent during the first hour of any day of the week gave its name to that day. During the 1st and 2nd century, the week of seven days was introduced into Rome from Egypt, and the Roman names of the planets were given to each successive day.</p>\r\n\r\n			<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="height:119px; width:485px">\r\n				<tbody>\r\n					<tr>\r\n						<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n						<td><img alt="" src="http://i.myniceprofile.com/1388/138879.gif" style="height:106px; width:235px" /><img alt="" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQmANVrgs1mQ2dMwNNN4u8FIb9uF7ieg-3NM2OOte_OtwhbmKRLAA" style="height:106px; width:235px" /></td>\r\n					</tr>\r\n				</tbody>\r\n			</table>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '[SUBJECT]: This placeholder will use for Subject of Newsletter.\r\n[USER]:This placeholder will use for user`s Name.\r\n[Email]:This placeholder will use for user`s Email.\r\n[FORWARD]:This placeholder will use as link of forward to friend.\r\n[UNSUBSCRIBE]:This placeholder will use as link of unsubscribe this newsletter.', 'Sunday is a day that have very restful for everyone. Enjoy Your sweet Sunday.', 1, '2015-01-09 13:10:05', '2014-12-25 14:32:11'),
